    CSVFileDownload
    Task used to read the content of the CSV file that is intended to be downloaded.

    Task used to treat the uploaded CSV file transforming all the uris it contanins in shortened uris.
    FileUploadController
    Class in charge of controling the upload of a CSV file with a list of urls, and treat this file in order to generate a new CSV file by creating shortened urls fo the original urls.
